article.headline: Langston Reynolds scores 31, Northern Colorado defeats Prairie View A&M 114-98
article.description: — Langston Reynolds scored 31 points as Northern Colorado beat Prairie View A&M 114-98 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Langston Reynolds scores 31, Northern Colorado defeats Prairie View A&M 114-98
article.story: GREELEY, Colo. -- — Langston Reynolds scored 31 points as Northern Colorado beat Prairie View A&M 114-98 on Saturday night. Reynolds had six rebounds for the Bears (5-2). Isaiah Hawthorne and Broc Wisne added 17 points apiece. Nick Anderson led the Panthers (1-5) with 32 points. Jordan Tillmon added 22 points and Marcel Bryant finished with 17 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
